channel.title: Cant get scar to keep going
channel.description:
i need help i been trying to leech some free east varrock miners/w bankers but it always starts and says
"Successfully compiled Successfully executed"
and if it doesnt say that it either goes over the ore, lags and does nothing more or randomly keeps clicking to run south untill i got no more land to run on.
So if anyone could sort me out with this things and plz no one calling me a noob because i already know i am. :rolleyes:
Plz and thank you. :D

item.title: Cant get scar to keep going
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Use the “repeat” and “until {CONDITION HERE}” functions. You can use “until False” or “until IsFKeyDown(5)”. That will stop when the f5 key is pressed.
